{"type":"text","timestamp":1781128736367,"sessionID":"ses_14c74eea6ffemTvYGOsUhNiPQp","part":{"id":"prt_eb38baca1001oubBfdcNN8xRjr","messageID":"msg_eb38b59ca001KeI0z1jES5QfK2","sessionID":"ses_14c74eea6ffemTvYGOsUhNiPQp","type":"text","text":"The memory trigger lookup rejected the caller-provided session id because it is not server-managed; I’m continuing with the command-provided lineage id for artifact metadata and not using it for Spec Kit Memory session-scoped calls.","time":{"start":1781128735905,"end":1781128736355},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_09395bb8dce05b43016a29de1e8a74819194994982ca79bb02","phase":"commentary"}}}}
